snippet.title: Gori Cuddly Carnage - New Level Reveal Trailer | The Indie Horror Showcase 2023
snippet.description:
Play as a badass murder-kitty on a death-dealing hoverboard in Gori: Cuddly Carnage, a third-person ‘skate ‘n’ slash’ set in a neon-glowing futuristic world filled with intense destruction and fast-paced combat.

Gori: Cuddly Carnage is coming to PC, Nintendo Switch, PlayStation 4, PlayStation 5, Xbox Series X|S, and Xbox One.
